@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei

actor "学生用户" as Student
node "浏览器客户端\nVue 3 页面" as Browser
node "后端应用服务\nSpring Boot REST API" as Backend
database "MySQL 数据库\n成长业务数据" as DB
cloud "OpenAI-compatible\nAI 服务" as AI
node "本地/课程实验环境\nJDK + Node + Maven/npm" as Env

Student --> Browser : 页面访问与操作
Browser --> Backend : HTTP/JSON 请求
Backend --> DB : 读写用户、画像、目标、任务、随记、诊断数据
Backend --> AI : 画像抽取、随记抽取、阶段诊断、任务草案
Env .. Browser : 前端运行
Env .. Backend : 后端部署
Env .. DB : 数据库存储
@enduml
